</a>-Â <a href="http://www.hangthebankers.com/uk-inquiry-into-iraqi-prisoner-deaths-reveals-evidence-of-torture/" target="_blank">UK inquiry into Iraqi prisoner deaths reveals evidence of &#8216;torture&#8217;</a></strong></p>
